{"tid":390382,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［DIY撚］自制無線藍牙喇叭","createTime":"2017-09-07T05:18:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-07T05:18:28.000Z","uid":26449,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6ce4f7a61cbbfda7e7633e3f4d386e1221daea48","tid":390382,"uid":26449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T05:18:28.000Z","msg":"DIY 無線藍牙MP3喇叭<br />\n<br />\n是咁的，小弟有一鋪DIY癮，<br />\n出去買，不如自己整！<br />\n上次做左個MP3機，其實係買左多材料順便整。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/381993/page/1?ref=ios \" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/381993/page/1?ref=ios </a><br />\n<br />\n今次先係主角，無線藍牙MP3喇叭。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/07/131328_656c5042af16e276bbbdb77e94ca69bc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F07%2F131328_656c5042af16e276bbbdb77e94ca69bc.jpg&h=32e070d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n材料：<br />\nMP3模塊 $35<br />\n喇叭 $15<br />\n3000mAh鋰電池 $20<br />\n訂做亞加力膠板 $20<br />\n螺絲 $0<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/07/131227_ba29dfe2935f67cd8e8150104a97dcd5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F07%2F131227_ba29dfe2935f67cd8e8150104a97dcd5.jpg&h=de8d3358&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同上次塊板一樣都係搭載左充電功能，可以慳返唔少功夫。<br />\n可插卡、USB、藍牙接收、FM功能。<br />\n<br />\n喇叭，質素一般，太大聲會拆拆地，可能太細個。<br />\n<br />\n亞加力膠板用電腦畫完圖就淘寶搵廠做激光切割，質素一般但可以接受<br />\n<br />\n去片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2B303kzT99k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2B303kzT99k&d=sO0Px8KvEZm8glN2KaOhaU%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=4a4b44ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2B303kzT99k</a>"}]}